1387
01:52:37.637 --> 01:52:40.173
Hello, Z-Zebra.
Ça va?


1388
01:52:41.138 --> 01:52:44.005
Je pense, leader.
Restez à l'écoute.


1389
01:53:10.682 --> 01:53:12.720
Goner Z
-Zebra.

1390
01:53:16.141 --> 01:53:18.760
