depuis un certain temps.


1396
01:53:47.937 --> 01:53:50.093
Goner, L
-Leather.

1397
01:53:57.729 --> 01:54:01.309
OK, Dave. Touché mais pas brisé.

1398
01:54:01.438 --> 01:54:04.223
